tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ShippingRates (
    rate_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    distance_range VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    weight_range VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    rate DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    company_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (company_id) REFERENCES ShippingCompanies(company_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Shipments (
    shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    distance DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    weight DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    speed_id INT,
    shipping_cost DECIMAL(15,2) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (speed_id) REFERENCES DeliverySpeeds(speed_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ShippingCost (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  distance_id INT,
  weight_id INT,
  speed_id INT,
  cost FLOAT,
  FOREIGN KEY (distance_id) REFERENCES Distance(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (weight_id) REFERENCES Weight(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (speed_id) REFERENCES DeliverySpeed(id)
);
